{"tid":2352332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"協助12港人家屬　人權律師盧思位被中共吊銷執業證書","createTime":"2021-01-04T03:24:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T03:46:22.000Z","uid":6497,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7439bcac3cbcb25aa5d3ac3eb80b0532b8d4aa","tid":2352332,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:24:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568486-20210104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568486-20210104.htm&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=0bdb48bf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1568486-20210104.htm&h=de0b4888\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1568486-20210104.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n「深圳12港人案」其中一名家屬委託的四川律師盧思位，今日收到四川省司法廳通知，計劃吊銷他的律師執業證書。<br />\n<br />\n司法廳指，調查發現盧思位在網上多次發表不當言論，時間跨度長、發文數量多，嚴重損害律師行業形象，造成惡劣社會影響，行為觸犯《律師法》和《律師執業管理辦法》相關規定。<br />\n<br />\n當局表示，盧思位有權陳述、申辯和聽證，如果要求舉行聽證，需要在三日內提出。"},{"pid":"cfdae685b8d48b469f4154fe08478a698a0ef094","tid":2352332,"uid":64603,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dxO4ybm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdxO4ybm.jpg&h=c95bb906&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"36299cc1e3cef54004ba142a7491996a5b2ec431","tid":2352332,"uid":148756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T03:33:21.000Z","msg":"Twitter news:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/jooeysiiu/status/1345933117484388352?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjooeysiiu%2Fstatus%2F1345933117484388352%3Fs%3D19&d=qAbY1fQWWFezl0O3VAvZyR5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=7b16681a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjooeysiiu%2Fstatus%2F1345933117484388352%3Fs%3D19&h=d502c73e\" data-auto-link